<h1 class="step">Continue installing or upgrading Tails</h1>

With this USB image, you can either:

- Upgrade your Tails USB stick and keep your Persistent Storage.

  * [[Upgrade from your Tails|doc/upgrade/tails]]

  * [[Upgrade from Windows|doc/upgrade/windows]]

  * [[Upgrade from macOS|doc/upgrade/mac]]

  * [[Upgrade from Linux|doc/upgrade/linux]]

- Install a new Tails USB stick.

  * <span class="button">[[Install from Windows|install/windows]]</span>

  * <span class="button">[[Install from macOS|install/mac]]</span>

  * <span class="button">[[Install from Linux|install/linux]]</span>

  * <span class="button">[[Install from Debian or Ubuntu using the command line and GnuPG|install/expert]]</span>

To burn a Tails DVD, download our [[ISO
image|download-iso]] instead.

